title: Kim Kardashian Shows Off Her 1980s 'Barbie' Magazine Debut
text:
Kim Kardashian Shows Off Her 1980s 'Barbie' Magazine Debut February 9, 2017 @ 5:09 AM By Kathy Campbell Kim Kardashian attends the Balenciaga show as part of the Paris Fashion Week Womenswear Spring/Summer 2017 on October 2, 2016 in Paris, France. Credit: Bertrand Rindoff Petroff/Getty Images 
So sweet! Kim Kardashian took to Snapchat on Wednesday, February 8, to show off her magazine debut in a 1980s issue of Barbie . PHOTOS: Kim Kardashianâ€™s Toned-Down Style 
"You guys, my first debut was in 1988 in Barbie magazine," she said as she flipped through the issue. "Look at what a star, reading star maps." 
The photo shoot showed the future reality TV star wearing an oversize white bow in her hair as she checked out some Los Angeles landmarks in the "Special California Issue." 
Kardashian, who would have been about 8 years old in the pics, posed with Mickey Mouse ears beside a star on the Hollywood Walk of Fame, checked out celebrity handprints at Grauman's Chinese Theater and visited Universal Studios Hollywood. A video posted by Kim Kardashian Snapchats (@kimksnapchats) on Feb 8, 2017 at 4:37pm PST A video posted by Kim Kardashian Snapchats (@kimksnapchats) on Feb 8, 2017 at 4:39pm PST 
"Look, I love L.A. How cute," the 36-year-old said in a second video. You May Also Like
